word_mean_info__list.difference: 指完全达到预定的条件、要求、标准或期望、心愿等。
指最低限度地达到预期的标准，或强调要达到这个标准的困难。
与satisfy基本同义，但侧重指实现的情况好于一般标准。

bilingual.source: Their stories satisfy us and help us feel safe.
bilingual.target: 他们的故事让我们满足并感到安全。

bilingual.source: Charles Schulz drew the cartoons to satisfy people as well as children.
bilingual.target: 查尔斯·舒尔茨画漫画来满足大人和孩子。

bilingual.source: We need to satisfy the needs of our customers.
bilingual.target: 我们需要满足客户的需求。

bilingual.source: This cake can satisfy my craving for sweets.
bilingual.target: 这个蛋糕能满足我的甜食欲望。

bilingual.source: The assets were liquidated to satisfy the creditors.
bilingual.target: 资产被清算以满足债权人。

bilingual.source: He works hard to satisfy the needs of his family.
bilingual.target: 他努力工作以满足家庭的需要。

bilingual.source: They held a lavish party to satisfy vanity.
bilingual.target: 他们举办了一个豪华的派对来满足虚荣心。

bilingual.source: The company aims to satisfy the needs of its customers.
bilingual.target: 公司旨在满足其客户的需求。

bilingual.source: He bought the latest phone just to satisfy vanity.
bilingual.target: 他买了最新款的手机只是为了满足虚荣心。

bilingual.source: Her demands are too unreasonable, no one can satisfy her.
bilingual.target: 她的要求太矫情了，没人能满足她。

list.abstract: 《Satisfy》是由歌手Ashanti演唱的一首英文歌曲，于2008年10月14日发行，收录于专辑《The Vault》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, then let me satisfy your curiosity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么让我来满足你的好奇心。

yingyinNormal.en: But no Chandler is in an accident and can't perform sexually and he would want you to take a lover to satisfy the needs that he can no longer fulfill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 说不定钱德发生意外，丧失了性能力，他要你找个爱人，满足他无法满足你的那个部份。

yingyinNormal.en: Prove it in court. Sure. But before you do something to satisfy your ego, I'd check with my client first.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在法庭上证明吧。肯定的，但在你满足你的自负之前，我先问问我的委托人。

yingyinNormal.en: It might explain why the two of you have created an ersatz homosexual marriage to satisfy your need for intimacy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这或许可以解释为何你们俩建立一段同性恋代替性婚姻关系来满足自己对亲密关系的饥渴。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm in kind of in a delicate spot, stuck between my wife and the guy next door, but I'm pretty sure I can satisfy them both simultaneously.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在处境有点微妙，夹在老婆和隔壁的哥们之间左右为难，不过我有把握同时满足他们两个。

yingyinNormal.en: The father of the grid recognized the danger of using finite resources to feed his creation, and we're still searching for clean, renewable sources of power to satisfy our boundless desire for electricity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 万物之王意识到用有限资源养育他的子民的危险，我们还会继续寻找清洁可再生能源，以满足我们对电的无限需求。

yingyinNormal.en: It's just to make a record, to satisfy the complaining gentleman.
yingyinNormal.zh: 做个记录而已，给举报人一个交代。

yingyinNormal.en: But the danger is, once we begin the rebels will not stop calling for retribution. Thirst for blood is a difficult urge to satisfy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是危险在于，一旦我们处死这些人，叛军们就停不下来了，杀人是会上瘾的。

examination_example.sentence: That said, there is a way in which grade forgiveness <highlight>satisfies</highlight> colleges' own needs as well.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 也就是说，等级宽恕也是满足大学自身需求的一种方式。

examination_example.sentence: The need to know is so strong that people will seek to <highlight>satisfy</highlight> their curiosity even.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对知识的需求如此强烈，以至于人们会寻求满足他们的好奇心。

examination_example.sentence: Behavioral scientists tested students' willingness to expose themselves to unpleasant stimuli in an effort to <highlight>satisfy</highlight> curiosity.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 行为科学家测试了学生将自己暴露在不愉快刺激下以满足好奇心的意愿。

sense_info_list.en: make someone believe that something is true

word_usage.usage:
“感到满意”用be satisfied，后常接with引导的短语，注意句子的主语只能是人。
示例： 我对这个计划很满意。
误 The plan is satisfied with me.
正 I am satisfied with the plan.
